rce/Great_Britain\", \"score\": 0.7758430546206179, \"rank\": 0.288917930273441, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"silvers\", \"from\": 769, \"to\": 776}, {\"ngram\": \"the velodrome\", \"from\": 780, \"to\": 793}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Schrager finished second in the women's C1-3 3000m individual pursuit, while Bate and pilot Chris Latham were runners-up in the men's B 4000m individual pursuit.\", \"from\": 796, \"to\": 957, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 888, \"end\": 900, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Latham_(rugby_union)\", \"score\": 0.9409601594669764, \"rank\": 0.05798394290811248, \"text\": \"Chris Latham\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13415036\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Latham_(rugby_union)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Latham_(rugby_union)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Schrager\", \"from\": 796, \"to\": 804}, {\"ngram\": \"the women's C1-3 3000m individual pursuit\", \"from\": 824, \"to\": 865}, {\"ngram\": \"runners-up\", \"from\": 906, \"to\": 916}, {\"ngram\": \"the men's B 4000m individual pursuit\", \"from\": 920, \"to\": 956}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Following a series of fitness setbacks, Cox, who has multiple sclerosis, appeared distraught as she hobbled from the track with assistance from members of the ParalympicsGB team.\", \"from\": 959, \"to\": 1137, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a series\", \"from\": 969, \"to\": 977}, {\"ngram\": \"fitness setbacks\", \"from\": 981, \"to\": 997}, {\"ngram\": \"Cox\", \"from\": 999, \"to\": 1002}, {\"ngram\": \"multiple sclerosis\", \"from\": 1012, \"to\": 1030}, {\"ngram\": \"the track\", \"from\": 1072, \"to\": 1081}, {\"ngram\": \"assistance\", \"from\": 1087, \"to\": 1097}, {\"ngram\": \"members\", \"from\": 1103, \"to\": 1110}, {\"ngram\": \"the ParalympicsGB team\", \"from\": 1114, \"to\": 1136}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think I got back on the bike two weeks ago,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1139, \"to\": 1196, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the bike\", \"from\": 1162, \"to\": 1170}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was in a boot four weeks ago.\", \"from\": 1197, \"to\": 1229, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a boot\", \"from\": 1207, \"to\": 1213}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It has just been a really rubbish year.\", \"from\": 1231, \"to\": 1271, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a really rubbish year\", \"from\": 1249, \"to\": 1270}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This time last year I could not walk because I had a really bad relapse that affected my right side.\", \"from\": 1272, \"to\": 1372, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a really bad relapse\", \"from\": 1323, \"to\": 1343}, {\"ngram\": \"my right side\", \"from\": 1358, \"to\": 1371}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It has been a roller-coaster, I guess that's MS.\", \"from\": 1374, \"to\": 1423, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1420, \"end\": 1423, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manuscript\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"MS.\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manuscript\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manuscript\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a roller-coaster\", \"from\": 1387, \"to\": 1403}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's just not what you want a year out from the Games.\", \"from\": 1424, \"to\": 1478, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1468, \"to\": 1477}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The fact that I got here was amazing in itself - I am just gutted I was able to ride a ride that was pretty great in the first round and then not go out there and show what I am capable of.\\\"\", \"from\": 1480, \"to\": 1671, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The fact\", \"from\": 1481, \"to\": 1489}, {\"ngram\": \"a ride\", \"from\": 1566, \"to\": 1572}, {\"ngram\": \"the first round\", \"from\": 1598, \"to\": 1613}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Leeds-born Cox was denied a restart as the fall was deemed not to be down to a mechanical fault.\", \"from\": 1673, \"to\": 1769, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Leeds-born Cox\", \"from\": 1673, \"to\": 1687}, {\"ngram\": \"a restart\", \"from\": 1699, \"to\": 1708}, {\"ngram\": \"the fall\", \"from\": 1712, \"to\": 1720}, {\"ngram\": \"a mechanical fault\", \"from\": 1750, \"to\": 1768}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She continued to receive treatment on the floor of the track centre long after the event had finished.\", \"from\": 1771, \"to\": 1873, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"treatment\", \"from\": 1796, \"to\": 1805}, {\"ngram\": \"the floor\", \"from\": 1809, \"to\": 1818}, {\"ngram\": \"the track centre\", \"from\": 1822, \"to\": 1838}, {\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 1850, \"to\": 1859}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I overcompensated and just could not balance on my weaker side.\", \"from\": 1875, \"to\": 1938, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my weaker side\", \"from\": 1923, \"to\": 1937}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was all over the shop.\", \"from\": 1939, \"to\": 1964, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the shop\", \"from\": 1955, \"to\": 1963}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The world record holder had looked odds-on to become GB's first medallist of the Games following her triumphs at Rio 2016 and Tokyo 2020.\", \"from\": 1966, \"to\": 2103, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2019, \"end\": 2021, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"score\": 0.9707623088384442, \"rank\": 0.02993425133249161, \"text\": \"GB\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\"}, {\"begin\": 2092, \"end\": 2097, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9997376845480924,