 and just could not balance on my weaker side.\", \"from\": 2552, \"to\": 2616, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my weaker side\", \"from\": 2601, \"to\": 2615}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was all over the shop.\\\"\", \"from\": 2617, \"to\": 2643, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the shop\", \"from\": 2633, \"to\": 2641}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Actor and martial artistJackie Chanwas part of the presentation party as Schrager received her landmark medal.\", \"from\": 2645, \"to\": 2755, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Actor\", \"from\": 2645, \"to\": 2650}, {\"ngram\": \"martial\", \"from\": 2655, \"to\": 2662}, {\"ngram\": \"artistJackie\", \"from\": 2663, \"to\": 2675}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 2684, \"to\": 2688}, {\"ngram\": \"the presentation party\", \"from\": 2692, \"to\": 2714}, {\"ngram\": \"Schrager\", \"from\": 2718, \"to\": 2726}, {\"ngram\": \"her landmark medal\", \"from\": 2736, \"to\": 2754}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 23-year-old, who has cerebral palsy, only joined the cycling programme in 2019, having never previously ridden.\", \"from\": 2757, \"to\": 2872, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"cerebral palsy\", \"from\": 2782, \"to\": 2796}, {\"ngram\": \"the cycling programme\", \"from\": 2810, \"to\": 2831}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She set a C2 world record of 3:45.133 in qualifying before clocking 3:51.129 in the final, just under 10 seconds slower than Chinese gold medallist Xiaomei Wang.\", \"from\": 2874, \"to\": 3035, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2999, \"end\": 3006, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"score\": 0.8926075295312802, \"rank\": 0.11933755118997004, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a C2 world record\", \"from\": 2882, \"to\": 2899}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If you'd asked me a year ago, I would have bitten your arm off to have one,\\\" Schrager said of the medal.\", \"from\": 3037, \"to\": 3142, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your arm\", \"from\": 3088, \"to\": 3096}, {\"ngram\": \"Schrager\", \"from\": 3115, \"to\": 3123}, {\"ngram\": \"the medal\", \"from\": 3132, \"to\": 3141}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I could feel she (Wang) was coming and I knew I did not have any more to give.\", \"from\": 3144, \"to\": 3223, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Wang\", \"from\": 3163, \"to\": 3167}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I gave it everything and I broke my world record in the process, I am so happy I did that.\", \"from\": 3224, \"to\": 3314, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 3234, \"to\": 3244}, {\"ngram\": \"my world record\", \"from\": 3257, \"to\": 3272}, {\"ngram\": \"the process\", \"from\": 3276, \"to\": 3287}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She was just better on the day.\\\"\", \"from\": 3315, \"to\": 3347, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the day\", \"from\": 3338, \"to\": 3345}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Two-time Paralympic champion Bate celebrated the fifth medal of his Games career.\", \"from\": 3349, \"to\": 3430, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Two-time Paralympic champion Bate\", \"from\": 3349, \"to\": 3382}, {\"ngram\": \"the fifth medal\", \"from\": 3394, \"to\": 3409}, {\"ngram\": \"his Games career\", \"from\": 3413, \"to\": 3429}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He and Latham were just over two seconds slower than Dutch duo Tristan Bangma and Patrick Bos, who won with a new world record of 3:55.396.\", \"from\": 3432, \"to\": 3571, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3439, \"end\": 3445, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Swayne_Latham\", \"score\": 0.9989933088850906, \"rank\": 0.0010073871270587455, \"text\": \"Latham\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q14128148\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Swayne_Latham\", \"dbpedi